node.text: real talk: pregnancy can be super challenging right now. with the stresses of trying to stay healthy, social isolation and baby showers being cancelled, moms-to-be aren't feeling the love they normally would! @schickintuition has ALWAYS cared for women, that’s why I’ve teamed up with them to curate 3 unique “shower” experiences that shower pregnant women with the love they deserve. check out @schickintuition’s IG guides for everything YOU need to shower yourself with love. #ad #intuitionmommyshower
